nto-microsofts-deal-with-inflection-ai-130038896.html"><ins>FTC发起了对微软与拐点AI的交易的反托拉斯调查</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-photography-gifts-for-dads-135953254.html"><ins>送给爸爸的最佳摄影礼物</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-cwa-forge-labor-neutrality-agreement-covering-all-zenimax-workers-212643324.html"><ins>Microsoft和CWA Forge劳动中立协议涵盖所有Zenimax工人</ins></a></p><p><em>您可以将这些报告直接直接发送到收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅！</em></a></p><p></p><h2 id="jump-link-boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss"><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><ins>波音公司的Starliner克服了最后一秒钟的问题与ISS停靠</ins></a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-phew">ph。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/23790600-24b1-11ef-9fff-83cf525d8699" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/23790600-24b1-11ef-9fff-83cf525d8699" style="height:348px;width:620px;" alt="Starliner的图像" data-uuid="bf51482f-2266-3dcf-b5a4-1f0498613a44"><figcaption></figcaption> <div class="photo-credit">NASA电视</div></figure></a><p>Starliner已<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><ins>成功与ISS停靠，但就像其发布一样，连接并非没有问题</ins></a>。出现故障推进器阻止了第一次尝试，但第二个是成功的。 Starliner船员将在接下来的八天里乘坐车站，然后我们都希望安全回到地球。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a> </p><h2 id="jump-link-starship-survives-re-entry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test"> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><ins>在成功的第四次飞行测试后，星际飞船幸存下来，在印度洋重新进入印度洋</ins></a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-more-milestones-for-the-heavy-vehicle">重型车辆的更多里程碑。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/4398e680-24b1-11ef-9776-cf88e5d0a91c" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/4398e680-24b1-11ef-9776-cf88e5d0a91c" style="height:328px;width:620px;" alt="星际飞船的形象" data-uuid="97d8a157-ac1f-3f64-a81c-e425b12d1225"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">太空探索技术公司</div></figure></a><p>SpaceX巨大的星际飞船火箭在<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><ins>推出和重新进入气氛后，在成功降落在印度洋之前就</ins></a>跳过了几个里程碑。返回旅程中存在一些问题，包括在下降时开始燃烧的襟翼。但是，SpaceX的情绪再次表现出如此多的功能后，可能是胜利的。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a> </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2 id="jump-link-apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac"> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><ins>据报道，苹果将为iPhone和Mac构建专用密码应用程序</ins></a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-are-1password-and-lastpass-at-risk-of-being-sherlocked">1Password和LastPass是否有被裁缝的风险？</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p> WWDC之前的一个较晚的谣言是，苹果将为<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><ins>iOS和MACOS建立自己的密码经理</ins></a>。该公司已经内置了一个复杂的密码管理器，但是有传言称独立应用程序将既易于使用又更大。如果是真的，很可能会促使人们担心第三方密码经理（例如1Password和LastPass）有被肌肉脱离空间的风险。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p>本文最初出现在https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-what-what-to-toppect-from-apples-big-event-11524145.html?src=rsss]>;]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-what-to-expect-from-apples-big-event-111524145.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 90D9F2B1-2305-420E-A6B4-A9A2DEF8E5EC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Daniel Cooper]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:15:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1717754134</ingested><modified> 2024-06-07T09：55：39+00：00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="899" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F1711a270-db12-11ee-86ce-4a7693cc0a77&amp;resize=1400%2C899&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=e55a3e1fb4793888b37885fe1dcd81a1f6a43fed" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content he